NAME
    Perinci::To::Text - Generate text documentation from Rinci package
    metadata

VERSION
    version 0.19

SYNOPSIS
     use Perinci::To::POD;

     # to generate text documentation for the whole module
     my $doc = Perinci::To::Text->new(url => "/Some/Module/");
     say $doc->generate_doc;

    You can also try the peri-doc script (included in the Perinci::To::POD
    distribution) with the "--format text" option:

     % peri-doc --format text Some::Module

    To generate a usage-like help message for a single function only, you
    can try Perinci::CmdLine, using it like this:

     my $cmd = Perinci::CmdLine->new(url => "/Some/Module/func");
     $cmd->run_help; # will print help text

